Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:55.99,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}重要時刻 請勿打擾！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.79,0:23:11.76,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就在 這雙手接觸的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.13,0:23:13.39,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}哎呀 嘁·嘁·嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:17.10,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}電燈泡出現啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:21.28,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這時機也太絕妙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:25.72,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}已經不能再猶豫不決了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:30.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\1c&HBBCDDA\3c&H2A353B}就算是那位傳聞中的大小姐 也一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.71,0:23:34.62,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\1c&HBBCDDA\3c&H2A353B}在這一刻面頰微紅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:40.18,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\1c&HBBCDDA\3c&H2A353B}想說卻說不出口的那句話
